Description: Fix CVE-2026-1527 CRLF injection in upgrade header
 Add validation for the upgrade option in Request constructor using
 isValidHeaderValue() to prevent CRLF injection attacks that could
 enable protocol smuggling to internal services such as Redis,
 Memcached, or Elasticsearch.
Origin: upstream, https://github.com/nodejs/undici/commit/77594f923cef4c27ee0bad365e7b4c44a199edae
Author: Matteo Collina <hello@matteocollina.com>
Bug: https://github.com/nodejs/undici/security/advisories/GHSA-4992-7rv2-5pvq
CVE: CVE-2026-1527

